<p>Hello <%= @resource.to_s %>,</p>

<p>Someone has requested a password reset. You can do this through the link below.</p>

<p><%= link_to 'Change my password', edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token), style: "color: #F7525E;border: 1px solid #F7525E;padding: 6px 8px;border-radius: 4px" %></p>

<p>If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.</p>
<p>Your password won't change until you access the link above and create a new one.</p>
